<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Where a preventive distillation operation for table wine and wine suitable for yielding table wine as provided for in Article 38 of Regulation (EEC) No 822/87 is opened, it shall be carried out in accordance with the provisions of this Regulation. </inglise>
